lead_paragraph: A Jamaican athlete is among those who have failed a doping test after samples were re-examined from the 2008 Beijing Olympic games in the wake of a drugs scandal, sources familiar with the case have told Reuters.

headline.print_headline: Jamaican Athlete Among Positive Tests From 2008 Olympics: Sources
